The door of the ship slid open allowing KitKat entry, Phobia kept his 
distance, he remembered how she looked when she wanted something, she 
had that look now but he sensed a certain desperation to her voice.

"What can I do for you my sweet?" he said, adressing KitKat with the 
tone of a subordinate.

--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, logomorph@h... wrote:
> ::KitKat:;
> 
> She ran untill she came up on the ship.  She ran up the entrace 
ramp.
> "Phobia, it's me, KitKat, Let me in."  she said slightly out of 
> breath from running.
